abstract: Zach Scott, Jalen Warren and Caleb Catto combined for 50 points Saturday and Florida Gulf Coast topped NAIA Saint Thomas (Fla,) 84-62, ending a six-game losing streak.
snippet: Zach Scott, Jalen Warren and Caleb Catto combined for 50 points Saturday and Florida Gulf Coast topped NAIA Saint Thomas (Fla,) 84-62, ending a six-game losing streak.
lead_paragraph: FORT MYERS, Fla. — Zach Scott, Jalen Warren and Caleb Catto combined for 50 points Saturday and Florida Gulf Coast topped NAIA Saint Thomas (Fla,) 84-62, ending a six-game losing streak.
headline_main: Scott Scores 19, FGCU Ends 6-Game Losing Streak 84-62
headline_print_headline: Scott Scores 19, FGCU Ends 6-Game Losing Streak 84-62

abstract: Jordan Miller registered 17 points as George Mason defeated Maryland-Baltimore County 69-53 on Saturday.
snippet: Jordan Miller registered 17 points as George Mason defeated Maryland-Baltimore County 69-53 on Saturday.

abstract: Saint Louis coach Travis Ford described his team's 66-63 win over Kansas State on Saturday night as the best win of the season.

abstract: D'Shawn Schwartz could not recall hitting a shot like this one, with his team trailing as the final seconds ticked away. And when the ball fell through the net as the buzzer sounded, it set off a celebration as wild as Colorado's overtime victory against No. 13 Dayton.
snippet: D'Shawn Schwartz could not recall hitting a shot like this one, with his team trailing as the final seconds ticked away. And when the ball fell through the net as the buzzer sounded, it set off a celebration as wild as Colorado's overtime victory ...
lead_paragraph: CHICAGO — D'Shawn Schwartz could not recall hitting a shot like this one, with his team trailing as the final seconds ticked away. And when the ball fell through the net as the buzzer sounded, it set off a celebration as wild as Colorado's overtime victory against No. 13 Dayton.
headline_main: Schwartz Hits 3 at Buzzer, Colorado Stuns Dayton 78-76 in OT
headline_print_headline: Schwartz Hits 3 at Buzzer, Colorado Stuns Dayton 78-76 in OT

abstract: The Detroit Pistons swept the season series with Chicago in 2018-19. Now the Bulls are a win away from returning the favor.
snippet: The Detroit Pistons swept the season series with Chicago in 2018-19. Now the Bulls are a win away from returning the favor.
lead_paragraph: DETROIT — The Detroit Pistons swept the season series with Chicago in 2018-19. Now the Bulls are a win away from returning the favor.

abstract: A bloc of eight countries will rename their French-backed currency and France will scrap a contentious requirement for reserve deposits.
snippet: A bloc of eight countries will rename their French-backed currency and France will scrap a contentious requirement for reserve deposits.
lead_paragraph: DAKAR, Senegal — A bloc of West African states took a step away from a French-backed regional currency that dates back to the colonial era, making a significant symbolic break from the past.

abstract: Rhyne Howard scored 19 of her 29 points in the fourth quarter, including the go-ahead jumper with 2 seconds left, to help No. 14 Kentucky hold off California for a 63-61 win on Saturday.

abstract: The commander-in-chief of the Chilean Air Force has warned that the struggle to recover the remains of a Hercules that crashed en route to the Antarctic two weeks ago could make it difficult to ever determine what happened to the plane.
snippet: The commander-in-chief of the Chilean Air Force has warned that the struggle to recover the remains of a Hercules that crashed en route to the Antarctic two weeks ago could make it difficult to ever determine what happened to the plane.
lead_paragraph: SANTIAGO — The commander-in-chief of the Chilean Air Force has warned that the struggle to recover the remains of a Hercules that crashed en route to the Antarctic two weeks ago could make it difficult to ever determine what happened to the plane.
headline_main: Chile's Air Force Chief: 'We May Never Know' What Happened to Lost Hercules
headline_print_headline: Chile's Air Force Chief: 'We May Never Know' What Happened to Lost Hercules
